## Summary

| Use Case | License Required | Cost |
|----------|------------------|------|
| Personal, non-commercial | Personal License | **Free** |
| Professional, commercial | Professional License | **Paid (one-time)** |
| Organization (5+ users) | Enterprise License | **Contact us** |

---

## 1. Definitions

**"Software"** means Voice Keyboard application and all associated files, documentation, and updates.

**"Licensor"** means Alex Mak, the copyright holder.

**"Personal Use"** means use by an individual for private, non-commercial purposes on devices owned by that individual.

**"Professional Use"** means any use in connection with employment, business activities, freelance work, or any activity that generates or supports revenue.

**"Enterprise Use"** means use by an organization, company, or entity with more than 5 individuals using the Software.

**"Competing Product"** means any product or service that provides voice-to-text, speech recognition, or dictation functionality.

---

## 2. License Grants

### 2.1 Personal License (Free)

Subject to the terms of this Agreement, Licensor grants you a free, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the Software for Personal Use only.

**You MAY:**
- Install and use the Software on your personal devices
- Make copies for backup purposes
- Modify the Software for your personal use

**You MAY NOT:**
- Use the Software for any Professional or commercial purpose
- Redistribute the Software or modifications
- Remove or alter any license notices

### 2.2 Professional License (Paid)

A Professional License is required for any Professional Use of the Software.

**Professional License grants you the right to:**
- Use the Software for Professional and commercial purposes
- Install on multiple devices owned or controlled by you
- Receive updates for 1 year from purchase date

**Professional License does NOT allow:**
- Redistribution or resale of the Software
- Creating Competing Products based on the Software
- Transferring the license to another person or entity
- Use by multiple individuals (each user needs their own license)

**Pricing:** See https://voice-keyboard.app/pricing

### 2.3 Enterprise License (Contact Sales)

Organizations with 5 or more users must obtain an Enterprise License.

**Enterprise License includes:**
- Volume licensing for your organization
- Priority support
- **Optional:** Administrative dashboard for compliance monitoring
- **Optional:** Audit logs of Software usage within your organization
- Custom deployment options
- Dedicated account manager

**Enterprise features (optional add-ons):**
- Usage analytics and reporting
- Centralized configuration management
- Integration with corporate security systems
- Compliance reporting for regulated industries

**Contact:** enterprise@voice-keyboard.app

