c) Remove, alter, or obscure any copyright, trademark, or other proprietary notices;

d) Use the Software in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations;

e) Sublicense, rent, lease, or lend the Software to third parties;

f) Use the Software to process data in violation of privacy laws.

