## 5. Data Privacy

### 5.1 Personal and Professional Licenses

The Software processes audio locally on your device. No audio data or transcriptions are transmitted to Licensor or third parties.

### 5.2 Enterprise License

If your organization enables optional monitoring features:
- Administrators may access usage logs and transcription data
- Users will be notified when monitoring is active
- Data handling is subject to your organization's privacy policies
- Licensor does not receive or store this data

